-d%E1%BA%A1-phi%E1%BA%BFm-du-H%C3%A3n-giang-nguy%C3%AAn-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-9PECkGE_ZlaP8CgIDSHY3g">Hoạ Quảng Trị niết sứ Hồ Hữu Nguyên thu dạ phiếm du Hãn giang nguyên vận - 和廣治臬使胡友元秋夜泛遊捍江原韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-V%C4%83n-%C3%81i/H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-S%C6%A1n-thi/poem-e60kDOCsbytSX90efY86Ag">Hương Sơn thi - 香山詩</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-V%C4%83n-%C3%81i/author-HFcTQNxpTDpHMR0gzqMkMg">Phan Văn Ái</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Minh-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/K%E1%BB%87/poem-gO2Ou2ID7GmwSu7Fj5dTPA">Kệ - 偈</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Minh-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-9oAg30xeExsL6NJRaUaNeg">Minh Lương thiền sư</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Tr%E1%BB%AB-th%E1%BA%A3o/poem-xZ1BB9vkb6BZXgwohAcJ2A">Trừ thảo - 除草</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
